text: Rocquancourt is a former commune. It is found in the Normandy region in the Calvados department in the northwest of France. On 1 January 2019, it was merged into the new commune of Castine-en-Plaine.Arrêté préfectoral 19 December 2018, p. 10 ==Population== == References == Category:Former communes in Calvados
title: Rocquancourt
